{"tid":1216930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盧偉聰說若有人頭部中槍　呼籲向警方提供資料","createTime":"2019-06-13T11:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T11:32:59.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0cf0b044582a1beed1351b25d0dcc46751d73797","tid":1216930,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:27:43.000Z","msg":"提供資料比你拉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462706-20190613.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462706-20190613.htm&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmY26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=39531f55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462706-20190613.htm&h=6e95b8c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462706-20190613.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n警方昨日在金鐘一帶驅趕示威者，被指施放催淚彈前未有警告。警務處處長盧偉聰回應說，一般有時間的話，一定會先警告，但如果情況很危急，連警告都未能作出，有可能先行動其後再警告，昨日警方亦有多次舉旗及口頭警告。<br />\n<br />\n至於向示威者頭部開槍是否符合指引，盧偉聰說若有人頭部中槍，呼籲他向警方提供資料，讓他們檢查傷勢，讓他們進一步跟進，他不能憑空回答是否正確。<br />\n<br />\n被問到能否承諾不會使用實彈處理示威活動，盧偉聰說若有人投擲汽油彈或土製炸彈，他就不能這樣說，他保證警方一定克制，不會胡亂使用武力。"},{"pid":"47a6cd474d46ef054915659a2cd9bc0029162d42","tid":1216930,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:30:44.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4cff51ec91c683ae39d4ff6a185102b4d51b8fa","tid":1216930,"uid":15830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:31:44.000Z","msg":"提供資料比你地殺人滅口？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c55b6ccd85928afd3ab650e6c748ba3a040d077","tid":1216930,"uid":257238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:32:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}